	bumped Gtk+ requirement to 2.12.0 and readded DISABLE_DEPRECATED
	
	Patch from Jan Arne Petersen
	* gdl/gdl-dock-bar.c (gdl_dock_bar_instance_init),
	(gdl_dock_bar_destroy), (gdl_dock_bar_add_item):
