	* gdl/gdl-recent.c: Added James Willcox <jwillcox@cs.indiana.edu>
	(original author of gnome-recent on which gedit-recent is based, on
	which gdl-recent is based) to copyright list.
	* gdl/gdl-recent.h: Idem.

